Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Fallaina the Nous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.91,0:00:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't nous...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that strange creature in Lykos' island...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a nous here in the mud whale too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.43,0:00:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nous is something works like the heart for the ship on the sea of sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If the nous has been destroyed, the mud whale will sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Neli?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end you have found here...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.23,0:00:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl on the island, you must know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.12,0:00:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it's too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! For the sake of the mud whale!
