Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How can the mud whale shake like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:02:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So it started.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone will die after a few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's enjoy our playing until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's really going to sink?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you OK with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,OK or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really care yourself that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Human being is a burdensome creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The heart is annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Free us, with the power of the sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be saved from the suffering lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't judge it by your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What you want to throw away is yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is your own world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:03:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I will decide it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}We were born and raised on the mud whale,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}in such a small world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}What shocked us the most after we knew the world outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}is that outside the island,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}there are traces that people dying and living.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}And they are not simply the traces,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}but spectacular records that are swirling and sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Therefore, we scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}We are afraid how people... and the records had disappeared in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:40.25,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(982,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We must kill Fallaina completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}No matter how sad, how painful it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I will never resign my work as a recorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}We are not yet to finish our records!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you hurt our friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the minute she was on the mud whale,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.49,0:05:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,she became our friend, isn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does a person from our mother country try to stop us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't you a soldier with the mission to kill us all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:50.04,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You know if Fallaina is destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the mud whale and those who on it will sink together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that your aim?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:05:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,For me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You are... not... sinners...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You own something... that we lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Something important...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the hope... of this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it... now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You... you say we are the hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We have being carrying our sins... for a hundred years...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless we die... There is no way
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,for us to escape from this burden!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we are the sinners!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not something you can decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you presbyters think Taisha-sama, Sami and anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,deserve their deaths since they are the sinners?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think they are culpable of deaths?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened long long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Although those who attacked here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:06:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,also mentioned that there is no hope for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos, who come from the world outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes to love the mud whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that our hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The people from the world outside will
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,understand us one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it better to think this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we have some hopes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to run away from the hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I will protect Lykos and everybody else absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:32.93,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1050,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Kill Fallaina!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You must receive some treatment now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Be at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.49,0:07:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of us {\i1}Muin{\i0} were medical staffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shira'ai-sama! Nashiji-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Hakuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring her to the medical office!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear it a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, why you don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's not an easy decision...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But didn't you make up your minds?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hakuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I invited them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I have given you a hard time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.98,0:08:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The shake... has stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So he had done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The elderly must be scared at the last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.56,0:09:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happened with your eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fake paradise here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is going to decay like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Children of the whale are born with this curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be much easier to throw
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the rotten body and the unnecessary minds away together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we still have to live,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to stock some fun to have it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to have a boring live.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that shake?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the tool to destroy the lock of prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do then, we can't save Suo now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuz you fell down on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Lose some weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,S... Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.71,0:10:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hakuji-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been closing my heart and ruling others with my mind for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was for the sake of everybody, but it's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know what to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do for the island, for everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink this, and you will get calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise we will not confine you in your room anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Be easy and have a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to talk with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But what should we...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,After the group suicide have been turned down, what should we...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What should our children do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Neli?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did her go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There are lots of things I want to ask her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:12:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's nice to have the mud whale saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations! Our new chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That suits you, Su~o~sa~ma~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,From today, we are your aides.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.85,0:12:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.03,0:12:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the aides of Taisha-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually you have to appoint the new aides~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But we are in an emergency~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.29,0:12:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't got the permission of the presbytery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's just fine to report it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Though I am still inexperienced...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have an inexperienced chief at such a time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be dismissed immediately if you don't have the ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang, Kuchiba you are too straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't straight, but obviously...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're completely different before Taisha-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh...Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.09,0:12:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Suo~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,To see Lykos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:13:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she would tell us something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But how about the presbytery?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What? How innocent you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll report it later, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I couldn't trust the presbytery anymore after this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I understand they are for the sake of mud whale...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not good to split up under such an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We just get the information first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately that girl seems to be off her guard with Chakuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, Lykos is in our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the aides of chief follow the presbytery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's different this time~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for the sake of everyone on the mud whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,For our people, the presbytery and we are under the same principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\bord2\pos(932,1000)}νοῦς
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nous...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The presbytery tried to sink the mud whale by destroying that, you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Every ship has a nous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can fight the enemies off if we can destroy their nous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but... that means,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The people from Lykos' country will sink in the sand...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They have their means to return to the mother ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They even have a mother ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:23.13,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1176,1000)}σκύλος
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But if they lose the Skulax,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be pretty painful for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your country has only one battleship
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,called the {\i1}Sukilosu{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Don't break in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,To fulfill the plan of Chakuro,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,we need as much wisdom as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think Masoo has wisdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You should die out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to sleep until you recover from your injury!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already recovered!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You should shut up! You meathead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos, let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\bord2\pos(1156,1000)}νοῦς
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 8 ships equipped with nous in the empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:14:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There are as {\i1}many{\i0} as 8 big ships like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean there are {\i1}only{\i0} 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nous is a creature that absorbs emotions from human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who own nous are able to control the minds of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:15.90,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1282,1000)}νοῦς
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:15.90,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1056,1000)}λύκος
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They decided to secure Lykos the Nous first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.36,0:15:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ship was wrecked, and your fellows had been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A ship from the enemy state.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There are still other countries!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There are several.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There are as many as 8 ships that big.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There are numbers of guys like soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And there is a country where they belong to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There is an enemy state.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are even more countries?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I start to have a headache...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I will tell Oni afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So... They are our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the empire wants to destroy the mud whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:02.45,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1638,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Since other countries don't even know about the existence of Fallaina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does the empire want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,destroy the mud whale, Fallaina?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:10.69,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(740,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:10.69,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1398,1000)}νοῦς
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Fallaina is different from other nous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't absorb the feelings of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:19.12,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(502,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:19.12,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1074,1000)}νοῦς
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Fallaina is a heterogeneous nous different from the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,your ancestors are also...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.59,0:16:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:27.69,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1526,1000)}νοῦς
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It is said that your ancestors refused to be ruled by nous,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and chose to keep their own feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So the empire was using
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:37.77,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(292,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Fallaina, which can't fulfill its original purpose of {\i1}absorbing feelings{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,as a prison, to keep you imprisoned on the sea of sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We were... I was told that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the savages living with their own feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,live with suspicions and hates, in a small ship called Fallaina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a island like a living hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But since the enemy state has got the technology to travel over the sea of sand,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:07.60,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1466,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't give them the opportunity of seizing Fallaina.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,However the empire
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:14.93,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(846,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\bord2\pos(1502,1000)}fallaina
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,can not accept the Fallaina and the sinners of the whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So they have decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:23.37,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(864,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to annihilate the Fallaina, and to massacre all the ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,descendants of the sinners.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,B...But
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There are definitely people who are not our enemy somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere in the world outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not familiar with the other countries...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, a world full of enemies, and a world not
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,are totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.36,0:17:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's enemy is our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It is possible that somebody in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,will find us mud whale and accept our existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think we are able to wait until that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:18:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll have to endure the attacks from the empire before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think we can fight with hope
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,until we finally find our {\i1}companion{\i0} in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I would...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I would stake my life to cooperate with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a speech from the new chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what was the shake yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.89,0:18:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The new chief is there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Suo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I still believe what Lykos has told us,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is not the entire of the truth of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,For the empire, our existence
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,should have more meaning than wanting to wipe us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it is true that we have hopes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:19:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun has never betrayed us for even a single day!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The stars have never betrayed us for a single year!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They have never forgot to bring grace to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}Their mercy will never come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.02,0:19:15.17,Default,,0,0,105,,{\fs72}Neither the heaven nor the sand has cursed even a single person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unbelievable that the presbytery has permitted such an assembly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo, do your best~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to talk about the status we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and what should we do now in my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.76,0:19:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently, we had a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,some of you here are still in sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, it is not the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We have got information that they will attack again after 4 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.07,0:19:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't be trapped by the despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing we should do now, is to raise our faces
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:19:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and stand up together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't lose our confidence and give up. We should keep fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.69,0:20:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,until somebody in the world understands us and takes hands with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? What a good baby, it's fine now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to make it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1006,1000)\fs54\bord2}sentikinesis
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to rely on the thymia of the {\i1}Shirushi{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I always wanted to save you from your fates of short-living.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.38,0:20:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,While I haven't done anything for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've no choice but to ask you for so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the only guy who haven't accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys here have already accepted their curses of short-living for long!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.58,0:21:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They have also accepted the fate afterwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If only you can ask us to die for you, it'd be all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you also...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,willing to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shew!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.23,0:21:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Nobody knows whether the route we take is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}But after 4 days, we will face the all-out attack from Skulax.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:21:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}This is the only thing we are sure...
